videos.headline: Dormandy fumble recovered by UMASS
videos.description: Jesse Monteiro forces  Quinten Dormady to fumble, resulting in the first turnover of the game.

videos.headline: Chris Berman acts as UMASS special assistant coach
videos.description: ESPN's Chris Berman is on the UMASS sideline as an assistant coach.

videos.headline: Phillips comes up with 3rd down stop
videos.description: Kyle Phillips tackles Marquis Young for a loss of 6 yards on third down, forcing UMASS to punt.

videos.headline: Johnson Sacked by Ford on 3rd down
videos.description: Alexis Johnson sacks Andrew Ford to stop the driving UMASS offense.

videos.headline: Johnson takes Dormady pass 66 yards
videos.description: Brandon Johnson makes big run after catch to set up a Tennesse touchdown.

videos.headline: Kelly runs for 12 yard TD
videos.description: John Kelly scores Volunteers' first touchdown of the game with 12-yard run.

videos.headline: Comis runs for 5 yard TD
videos.description: Ross Comis' 5 yard touchdown run pulls UMASS within one point of Tennessee.

videos.headline: Byrd catches TD in corner of end zone
videos.description: Quinten Dormady hits Tyler Byrd in the end zone to put the Volunteers up 14-6 before the half ends.

videos.headline: Butch Jones Halftime Interview
videos.description: Butch Jones tells Olivia Harlan the Volunteers need to thrown the ball more in the second half.

videos.headline: Palmer makes toe-tapping TD catch
videos.description: Sadiq Palmer grabs Andrew Ford's pass along the sideline for a UMASS touchdown.

videos.headline: Isabella's 42-yard run
videos.description: Andy Isabella makes long run that brings UMASS into Tennessee territory

videos.headline: Vols hold off UMass
videos.description: Taylor Zarzour and Andre Ware discuss Tennessee's performance against UMass and the Volunteers' upcoming schedule.

videos.headline: Jones on his teams win
videos.description: Coach Butch Jones talks to Olivia Harlan about his teams 17-13 win.
